% following verses of the song. \beatson puts them back for the next verses
% (unless \showbeatsfalse is set in the main doc).
%
% Example usage:
%
%   |\[\bmc Am]Love \[\bm]is |\[\bm]great \[\bm]
%   and |\[bm]food \[bm]tastes |\[\bm]good \[\bm]
%
